15 Dollars ($750.00).
16 5. The ordinances may prescribe costs pursuant to the
17 provisions of Section 27-126 of this title or imprisonment not
18 exceeding sixty (60) days or both the such fine and imprisonment;
19 provided, that municipalities. Municipalities having only a
20 municipal court not of record shall not have authority to enact any
